add_relationship

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_relationship -  This method adds a relationship between two members of a family.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_relationship(string name,
string person,
string dest_name,
string dest,
string relationship)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the family
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person the relationship is from
%^BOLD%^dest%^RESET%^ - the person the relationship is to
%^BOLD%^dest_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the family the other person is in
%^BOLD%^relationship%^RESET%^ - the relationship they have to you
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if succcessful, 0 if not
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/inherit/club_family.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a relationship between two members of a family.
.EP

